                                    "text": "For a behind-the-scenes look at how your donation dollars are being put to work so far this summer, check out this short video, with commentary by facility manager Mike Bassoni. With time-lapse photography and regular documenting of the building process, we will continue to share photos, videos, drawings and more to update you on this historic project!
                                        "
