                                    "text": "We are grateful for your participation in this project. Yet we still need additional support to complete the construction. If you are interested in increasing your support please contact Joe Rosenthal, executive director of advancement, at <a href=\"mailto:joe.rosenthal@harker.org\">joe.rosenthal@harker.org</a>. You can also help by encouraging your fellow community members to join you in supporting the project!
                                        "
